The paper specifically focuses on data-to-text generation, which involves generating natural language descriptions from structured data. This falls under the subfield of NLP known as text generation or text-to-text generation.

Within cs.CL, the paper could also fall under the sub-categories of cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), or cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), as these are all relevant to the use of neural networks for text generation.
